2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"聽過曱甴係僲feel到殺氣<br />\n因為你想殺佢 你個心會跳得快少少  呢種曱甴係感應到<br />\n所以感應到而又有動靜果陣 佢地都走得快啲<br />\n<br />\n另外 見過條片  話有土著三人組係專拎獅子既食物<br />\n佢地三個發現獅子後  三個毫不畏懼咁走去獅子既獵物度<br />\n獅子見到無嬲反而離開咗俾佢地拎啲肉<br />\n但話拎肉既時間要少於三分鐘 否則獅子會唔驚/搞清咩狀況而襲擊返你<br />\n<br />\n以上係聽聞過既經驗"},{"pid":"8ea88c0f64022dc2c04b0da8c04831ac0f11f3f0","tid":685053,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7978d912d5c85f31bf318ac6885a7aae57ec83f9","tid":685053,"uid":2419,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T07:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/224703_92f96c441802229c1a6cdf84abf4f7bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F224703_92f96c441802229c1a6cdf84abf4f7bc.png&h=fa593680&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:28:12.000Z","msg":"請尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38dec8ed0be2dcd2146e4241ecb499bb22d9da6f","tid":685053,"uid":5374,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"打波個陣試過feel到 <br />\n有次特別強烈 你會知道你出左個球就食得屎 但明明無望到對手動作 點都要打另一種球路 <br />\n打完再望番對手真係準備捕我個球 有種心寒feel<br />\n利申 羽毛波"},{"pid":"571b78208a5704bfa43e386825543dbcc3051125","tid":685053,"uid":57269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"名校仔氣牆"},{"pid":"81afeedc1c3202f47ce2bee2ba7f8e3ab8516f65","tid":685053,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"平時喺公園見到雀仔就冇乜野<br />\n<br />\n但係試過個人一嬲 d雀仔即刻飛走"},{"pid":"285b50f1f27b9a5cd11047bf7d3df45575430ffa","tid":685053,"uid":71548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T21:30:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得有，或者話自己經常都感覺得到，當然好多時候自己嘅心理壓力都會放大左哩種感覺。<br />\n<br />\n利申：玩搏擊類運動"},{"pid":"96adcb5fac52da86ff2133292108